{"type": "article", "id": 29718, "title": "火山岩搁架", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-18T11:55:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160717210105izgk50aSDLrCwbuy.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>看腻了木制或者金属制的墙面搁架，为什么不试试用火山岩制成的呢？位于墨西哥的 <a href=\"http://www.peca.com.mx/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Peca</a> 工作室利用这种特别的材质设计了一套允许用户自由组合的搁架 Lava。它既可以布置成书架，也可以放在桌上用做收纳，甚至改造成一个小型的神龛。Peca 对这些原始而粗犷的火山岩进行了细致的加工，看起来方正美观。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717212633ukiYHs720maRC6nS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677262\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717212633nrSBNz2qmuIiM4wV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160717212633sBm90K2hip8trGXd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.688264\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607172126336fCuzRMBokXDj1Nv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.693154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}